quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  6,151,"Maaku : \"Aree mi janngana on ko Joomi mo Harmini e mon : ko nde kafidoton e Makko huunde, waЙ—anon jibimЙ“e mon Й“en moЖґЖґere. Wata on waru Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en kulol immorde e baasal. Ko Menen Arsikata on e kamЙ“e. Wata on Й“aЙ—to pankare Й—en ko feeГ±i e majje e ko wirnii. Wata waru wonkii ki Alla Harmini si wanaa e goonga. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  6,152,"Wata on Й“aЙ—to jawdi wonduЙ—o si wanaa hara ko no Й“uri moЖґЖґirde, haa o yottoo kellefuyee makko. Timminiree etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikirЙ—e= peesirde Й—en no nunЙ—iri. Men fawaa wonkii si wanaa ko ki townata. Si on wowlay nunЙ—ee hay si ko e hoore jom-Й“aЙ—todal. Ahadi Alla ndin hunnon. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on; belajo'o, on annditay"
  6,153,"E wonnde pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko laawol am focciingol, jokkee ngol ; wata on jokku laawoy senndaykoy on e laawol Makko ngol\". Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on ; belajo'o, on rentoto"
  6,154,"Refti Men Okki Muusaa Deftere nden timmirnde (neema) mo o moЖґЖґiniri, fensitunde kala huunde, ko nde peewal e yurmeende ; belajo'o, Й“e gomЙ—inay hawrygol e Jommi maЙ“Й“e"
  6,155,"Ndee Й—oo ko Deftere (Alqur'aana), Men Jippiinde ko nde barkinnde - jokkee nde, rentoЙ—on ; belajo'o, on yurmedon"
  6,156,"Fii wata on wi'oy : \"Defte Й—en ko e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i Jippinaa, ado amen, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e janngugol Й—e"
  6,157,"maa Й—um wi'on : \"Sinno menen, Deftere nden Jippinano e amen, men laatotono Й“urЙ“e Й“en Й—on feewude\". GomЙ—ii arii on immorde ka Joomi mon, Й“anngannduyee, e peewal, e yurmeende. Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГ±ude haa hewta on fennuЙ—o Aayeeje Alla Й—en o Й—uurnii Й—e. Arma Men YoЙ“iroya Й“en Й—uurnotooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en lepte bonЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo"
  6,158,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa nde Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en ara e maЙ“Й“e? Maa Joomi maa Ara? Maa yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ara? Г‘alnde yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ari, nafataa wonkii gomЙ—inal makki, ki laatanooki gomЙ—inki ko adii, maa ki faggitii e gomЙ—inal makki moЖґЖґere. Maaku : \"Habbitee! Menen ko men habbitiiЙ“e"
  6,159,"Pellet, Й“en sennduЙ“e diina mun kan, Й“e laatii feddeeji, a jeyaaka e maЙ“Й“e e huunde : Anndee fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e ko faade ka Alla. Refti O Humpita Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e golla"
  6,160,Kala arduЙ—o e moЖґЖґere hino woodani mo sappo yeru mayre ; kala kadi arduЙ—o e bone o yoЙ“itetaake si wanaa yeru makko. KamЙ“e Й“e tooГ±etaake
  6,161,"Maaku : \"Min, Joomi am Fewni lam faade e laawol focciingol, diina Г±iiЙ“uka, diina Ibraahiima, ooГ±iiЙ—o [e diina meere] ; o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  6,162,"Maaku : \"Pellet, julde am nden, e kirse am Й—en, e nguurndam am Й—am, e maayde am nden, ko All woodani, JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  6,163,"KafidiiЙ—o alanaa Mo! Ko Й—um mi yamiraa, ko mi woni arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  6,164,"Maaku : \"E ko tanaa Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata reweteeЙ—o, ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o kala huunde?! Kala wonkii faggitantaako si wanaa e hoore-makki : wonkii ronndotaako bone wonkii goo. Refti ko faade ka Joomi mon woni ruttorde mon, O Humpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mun"
  6,165,"Ko Kanko woni WaЙ—uЙ—o on lontiiЙ“e ka keydi, O ЖЃamtiri yoga mon dow yoga, darjaaji ; fii yo O Jarribo on e ko O Okki on. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—o lepte, Kanko kadi, ko O Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"